\begin_inset Formula $\pi$
\end_inset

 component (
\begin_inset Formula $g_{eff} = 0$
\end_inset

) remained in place and the two 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma$
\end_inset

 (
\begin_inset Formula $g_{eff} = \pm 1$
\end_inset

