noprefix "false"

\end_inset

, by grouping the 
\begin_inset Formula $m_J$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $g_L$
\end_inset

 factors of the individual levels into an effective g-factor. For a transition 
\begin_inset Formula $2 \rightarrow 1$
\end_inset

 the effective LandÃ© g-factor is given by equation 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq: g eff2"
plural "false"
